{"id":73687,"title":"Breast cancer: post-mastectomy radiotherapy reduces recurrence and mortality.","abstract":"The recent results of the Early Breast Cancer Trialists’ Cooperative Group meta-analysis have demonstrated that post-mastectomy radiotherapy reduces breast cancer recurrence and mortality in women with positive axillary lymph nodes—independently from the number of the lymph nodes involved—with no significant effect in patients with node-negative axillary status.","date":"2014-06-26","categories":"Neoplasms","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24889766","annotations":[{"name":"Radiation therapy","weight":0.822622,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Radiation_therapy"},{"name":"Breast cancer","weight":0.816298,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Breast_cancer"},{"name":"Breast","weight":0.722654,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Breast"},{"name":"Lymph node","weight":0.720049,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lymph_node"},{"name":"Lymph","weight":0.713367,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lymph"},{"name":"Cancer","weight":0.701843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cancer"},{"name":"Meta-analysis","weight":0.63907,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meta-analysis"},{"name":"Death","weight":0.456203,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Death"},{"name":"Woman","weight":0.262541,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Woman"},{"name":"Axilla","weight":0.111007,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Axilla"},{"name":"The Co-operative Group","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Co-operative_Group"},{"name":"Cooperative","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cooperative"}]}
